Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.65,0:00:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前情提要\NPreviously on Teen Wolf
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.65,0:00:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个本应该是锁着\NThat was supposed to be locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.92,0:00:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这是什么?        - 原子序数\N- What are those? - Atomic numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.60,0:00:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉\NKira.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.29,0:00:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得拍张你的照片\NI'm gonna take your picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,证明我们曾呆在一起过\NProof of our time here together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.37,0:00:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 艾萨克 - 艾萨克 开门啊\N- Isaac! - Isaac, open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.98,0:01:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾萨克?\NIsaac?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.68,0:01:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾萨克!\NIsaac!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.32,0:01:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他冻着了 爸爸 现在他冻得跟块冰似的\NHe's freezing. Dad, he's like ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾萨克 看着我 艾萨克\NIsaac, look at me. Isaac.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么了\NWhat's happening to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.49,0:01:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 艾萨克\NIsaac, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.49,0:01:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾萨克 听着 你得变身\NIsaac, listen. You have to turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.63,0:01:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着我\NLook at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得触发它 快 变身啊\NYou need to trigger it. Come on. Turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.67,0:01:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变身\NTurn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.77,0:01:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变啊\NTurn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.64,0:01:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看到他们了吗?\NDid you see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁?\NWho?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.45,0:01:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有五个\NThey were five of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.42,0:01:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一身黑\NThey wore black.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能...\NI couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.92,0:01:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看不到他们的脸 被遮住了\NI couldn't see their faces. They were covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.39,0:01:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思?像面具一样吗?\NWhat do you mean? Like masks?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中一个...我能看见他的眼睛\NOne of them... I could see his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.32,0:01:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黄绿色的\NThey were greenish-yellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是...\NLike a...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.06,0:01:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是萤火虫\NLike a firefly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:01:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,防御系统没被触发\NSecurity system wasn't triggered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.70,0:02:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们怎么进来的\NThen how did they get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.10,0:02:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们没进来\NThey didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.54,0:02:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们好像从阴影中走了出来\NIt was like they came out of the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那代表着什么吗?\NDo you know what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.55,0:02:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸?\NDad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.78,0:02:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,额... 我不太确定\NUm... I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着 你们两个...\NListen, the two of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.42,0:02:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你们两个在这件事情上对外界保持沉默一会儿\NI need you to keep this quiet for a few hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个人吗?\NFrom everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一天就够了\NJust 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.29,0:02:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们差点杀了他 爸爸\NThey could've killed him, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.73,0:02:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他们没这样做\NBut they didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.03,0:02:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信事出有因\NAnd I think there's a reason why.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.07,0:02:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们冲我来的\NI think they might have been after me.
