Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候到那儿的?\NSo when did you get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同时到的\NAt the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.61,0:03:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟谁同时?\NAt the same time as who?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我\NAt the same time as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巧合吗?\NBy coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巧合是什么意思?\NWhat do you mean coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:03:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在问你\NThat's what I'm asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个同时到达\NThe two of you arrived at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:04:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是巧合吗?\NWas that coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在问我吗?\NAre you asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得是在问我\NI think he's asking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想是在问你们两个\NI think he's asking the both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我来回答\NOkay, let me answer the questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对 我来问\NLet me ask the questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.03,0:04:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我总算弄清楚了\NJust so I have this absolutely clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴罗藏在学校的化学室里\NBarrow was hiding in the chemistry closet at the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人给他在黑板上留了信息\NSomeone left him a coded message on the blackboard
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他杀了基拉\Ntelling him to kill Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后巴罗带着基拉去了变电站\NThen Barrow took Kira to a power substation
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把她绑起来企图电死她\Nand tied her up with the intent of electrocuting her,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并且导致全城停电\Nwhich blacked out the entire town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听上去蛮对的\NSounds about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道他会带她去变电站\NHow did you know he'd take her to a power station?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他是电力工程师\NWell, 'cause he was an electrical engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他还能带她去哪呢?\NSo where else would he take her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.29,0:04:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是个推论而已 斯泰尔斯\NThat's one hell of a deduction there, Stiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我该说什么? 我学我爸\NYeah, what can I say? I take after my pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他恰恰在警局工作\NHe's in law enforcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯泰尔斯 嗯 你 你只要回答他就好\NStiles, just, uh... Just answer the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们猜的很准\NWe made a good guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.47,0:04:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个在干嘛\NWhat were the two of you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:04:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 吃比萨        - 吃寿司\N- Eating pizza. - Eating sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 吃寿司        - 吃比萨\N- Eating sushi. - Eating pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃了寿司跟比萨X2\NEating sushi and pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你信么?\NYou believe this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 自从斯泰尔斯学会说话以来\NTo be honest, I haven't believed a word Stiles has said
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说的话我一句话我都没信过\Nsince he learned how to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我觉得这些孩子在正确的时间\NBut I think these kids found themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正确的地点实现的自己的价值\Nin the right place at the right time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐在这的这个女孩真的是非常幸运\Nand that girl sitting there is very lucky for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 你记得是这样子的吗?\NKira, is that how you remember it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.28,0:05:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我能取回我的手机了么\NCould I get my phone back now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 不行\NSorry, but no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 等下副警带你回家\NKira, a deputy is going to take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过你先得完成这些文书工作\NBut we'll need you to fill out some paperwork first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:05:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯科特...\NScott...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你们为什么撒谎\NI don't know why you guys are lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者说为什么斯特林斯基愿意相信这些鬼话\NOr why Stilinski is content to listen to this crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是尽量记着\NBut try and remember something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假若关于巴罗的这个故事有一半是真的\NIf half this story about Barrow is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.65,0:06:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么不仅有人把他放了\Nthen not only did someone help set him loose,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且他只是这个盘游戏中的一个棋子\Nbut he was a pawn in their little game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个杀人犯已经够糟了\NA mass murderer is bad enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.09,0:06:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个被人控制的杀人犯呢?\NA mass murderer being controlled by someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更糟\NFar worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我懂了\NYeah, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 回去吧 明天还要上课\NAll right, go home. It's a school night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有五分钟上课\NClass starts in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为没电\NJust because there's no power
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别妄想学校停课\Ndon't expect there to be no school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三重否定 不错啊教练\NThat was a triple negative. Very impressive, Coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,点赞\NCopy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢\NOops!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 你从哪儿来\NHello. Where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 停下 停下\NNo. No. Stop. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛 我得和她谈谈\NWhat? I need to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.43,0:07:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 你得知道\NNo, you need to remember
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人留了信 让巴罗杀她\Nsomeone left a coded message telling Barrow to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要和她谈谈\NWhich is why I need to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯科特 别介\NScott, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我们弄清楚她不是另一个\NUntil we figure out if she's just another psychotic monster
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备杀死所有人的疯魔之前\Nthat's going to start murdering everybody,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我反对一切你跟她的交流\NI vote against any and all interaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.34,0:08:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果她喜欢我呢?\NWhat if she's like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩承受住了12.1亿瓦特的电流\NThat girl walked through 1.21 gigawatts of electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她跟你不一样\NShe's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就没有可移动发电机什么的吗?\NDon't you have portable generators or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不就是黑灯瞎火的聚会了吗 你又不需要这么多能源...\NIt's a black light party. It's not like you need a ton of power...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 好 我知道了\NOkay. Yeah, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.77,0:08:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑光聚会?\NBlack light party?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如说是被取消的聚会\NMore like canceled party.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我订的那个地方\NThe venue I booked
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最少还要一天才有电\Nwon't have power for at least another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想帮忙找个新地方吗?\NYou want help finding a new place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这重要吗?\NWhat's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个城就不可能有电了\NNothing in town's going to have power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说 谢了\NThanks anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想开个万圣节趴么?\NYou want to throw a Halloween party?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢?\NWhat's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你准备加入到年鉴俱乐部?\NYou gonna join the Yearbook Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做点有意思的事吧\NJust trying to do something nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛? 谁会在意?\NWhy? Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他啊\NHe does.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不懂 是吗?\NYou don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯科特根本不在意力量\NScott doesn't care about power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他关心的是人\NHe cares about people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想加入到他的狼群吗?\NYou want to be a wolf in his pack?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,努力做个高中生好吗\NTry being a human in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小甜心 看在这是我第一堂课\NSweetheart, since this is my first class
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我五年没教书了\Nand I haven't taught in five years,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想提醒你一件事\NI just want to remind you of one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.09,0:09:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让我难堪\NTry not to embarrass me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在说这些话之前你怎么不想想你今天穿的鞋子\NYou should've thought about that before wearing those shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 爱你      - 也爱你\N- Love you. - Love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈干嘛教生物?\NWhy's your mom teaching biology?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为哈里斯先生过去教生物\NBecause Mr. Harris used to teach biology.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.90,0:09:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到他跳槽\NUntil his new occupation...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干人祭了\NHuman sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啥? 我没杀他\NWhat? I didn't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.01,0:09:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉迪亚 怎么了?\NLydia, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一夜\NThe other night,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我救了一些人\NI helped save someone's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.56,0:09:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得很棒\NThat felt really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:10:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我看着你\NAnd I look at you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只能想起你帮忙杀了博伊德\Nand all I can think is that you helped kill Boyd.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不过是个坏小子 艾登\NYou're not just a bad boy, Aiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是一个坏人\NYou're a bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想和坏人在一起\NAnd I don't want to be with the bad guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我有个地方能让你办聚会\NI think I know a place where you can have your party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在不想谈\NI don't want to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想谈谈周五的微积分考试吗?\NWant to talk about the pre-cal test on Friday?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.75,0:11:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师说题目都出自书上\NThe teacher takes all the equations right out of the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有手机吗?\NDo you have your phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你看个别人都没看过的东西\NI'm going to show you something no one else has ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了巴罗以外\NNo one except for Barrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我拍张照 用上闪光灯\NTake a picture of me. And use the flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇\NWhoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这是什么?    - 我不知道\N- What is it? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几个月前就这样了\NIt started showing up a couple of months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有闪光灯开着才有\NIt only happens with the flash on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道为什么 但是巴罗知道这件事\NAnd I don't know how, but Barrow knew about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他用我的手机给我拍了照\NHe used my own phone to take pictures of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.03,0:11:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你想要回你手机的原因\NThat's why you asked for it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.40,0:11:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人看到过这些照片\NIf someone sees those pictures...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得拿回你的手机\NWe need to get your phone back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不给糖就捣蛋!\NTrick or treat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说那个原来住在这儿的人去哪儿了?\NWhere did you say the guy was who lives here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离开这儿了\NHe's out of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 赞\NOh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.21,0:13:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个能让你打开所有前门\NOkay, this one will get you into all of the perimeter doors,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个打开证物室\Nthis one into the evidence room,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而这个打开我爸的办公室\Nand this one's for my father's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会是偷来的吧 是吗?\NYou didn't steal these, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我用充磁机复制的\NNo. I cloned them using the RFID emulator.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是比偷还要糟?\NIs that worse than stealing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更聪明好吗\NIt's smarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯科特 我能问你些事吗?\NScott, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我会乖乖...\NOkay, I'll just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没跟他说吧\NYou didn't tell him anything, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.27,0:13:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照片的事情\NAbout the pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有 我只是告诉他你有些照片\NOh, no, I just said that you have some pictures of you on your phone
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,存在手机里 不想让别人看到\Nthat you didn't want anyone to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.51,0:13:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么类型\NWhat kind of pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:14:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裸照\NNaked pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真机智\NOh. Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.42,0:14:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行\NOkay, cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.69,0:14:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在基本上大家都在为没有电而苦恼\NOkay. So, now almost everybody's out dealing with the blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过前台还是有人的\NBut there's always somebody at the front desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,值班室有一两个值夜班的\NThere's Dispatch and usually a night shifter or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.90,0:14:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩得利用垃圾桶边上的服务窗口\NYou guys are gonna use the service door entrance by the dumpster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懂吗 没人用那个\NAll right? Nobody uses it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有任何人出现 我会给你发短信\NNow, I'll text you if anyone comes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 斯科特 如果你被抓了 我无能为力\NBut, Scott, if you get caught, I can't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸在接受被弹劾的调查\NMy dad's under investigation for an impeachment
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你爸 所以 发生什么事\Nbecause of your dad, so, if anything happens
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会跟你老死不相往来\NI will run and leave you both for dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懂了 谢啦 真的 兄弟\NGot it. Thanks. Seriously, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会问我爸 不过你懂的\NI'd ask my dad, but you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我懂了\NNo, I know. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 快去吧\NAll right, just, uh, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉\NKira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.63,0:15:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没电了\NIt's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:15:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得带走\NWe have to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 他们会知道手机不见的\NNo, they'll know it's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们怎么给它充电?\NHow do we charge it if the power's out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看能不能找到充电线\NSee if you can find a charger cable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.98,0:16:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了\NAwesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.89,0:16:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是谁?\NWho's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我\NMe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和我爸\NMe and my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点 快点\NCome on, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,见鬼\NAh, hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点 快点啊\NCome on. Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.57,0:17:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧 斯科特\NCome on, Scott.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我肯定会后悔的\NOkay, I'm so going to regret this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.19,0:17:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 嘿 谢天谢地你在这里\NHey, hey. Wow!Thank God you are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 感谢主\NOh, boy! Thank the lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想干嘛 斯泰尔斯\NWhat do you want, Stiles?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.70,0:17:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天\NOh, jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.94,0:17:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是 就是想了想案件\NI was just... I was thinking on the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.27,0:17:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该把我的想法告诉你\NI was thinking I should clue you in on my thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是这样想的\NHere's my thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:17:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想呢\NI was thinking this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为那个巴罗\NI was thinking that Barrow, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想巴罗是在学校收到\NI was thinking that Barrow received the information
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去杀谁的信息对吗\Nabout who to kill at the school, right, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我在想也许是有人\NSo I was thinking maybe the person who
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给了他信息\Ngave him that information,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注意这点\Ncheck this out,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许实际上这个人\Nmight actually be someone
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在学校\Nat the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的想法\NAnd that's, uh, my thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开机了\NIt's on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开机了\NIt's on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说的对\NYou're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是吗  -是的\N-I am? -Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们昨晚已经开始调查\NWe, uh...We started looking for links
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴罗与教职员和学生间的联系点了\Nbetween Barrow, faculty and students last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你已经 知道这情况了\NSo you already, then, know that stuff? Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经想到了\NYou already thought of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.75,0:18:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你爸想到的 -哦\N-Your dad did. -Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.86,0:18:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有用的建议之一\NHis one useful suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗 你对我爸的这种态度\NYou know, this attitude that you have toward my dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以装出一副\NYou can dress it up to all
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看似很专业的样子\Nthe professional disapproval that you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:18:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我知道你讨厌他的真正原因\NBut I know the real reason why you don't like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这吗?\NIs that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 因为他知道了你不想让他知道的事\NYeah. Because he knows something\Nthat you don't want him to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且你猜怎么着\NAnd guess what.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.65,0:19:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道\NI know it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧 斯泰尔斯\NGo home, Stiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚有宵禁\NThere's a... There's a curfew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们做到了 所有照片都删掉了\NWe did it. All the pics deleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是刺激死了\NThat was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说 有些怕怕 真的怕怕\NI mean, terrifying. Completely terrifying...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.66,0:19:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但蛮刺激的\NBut kind of awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前还从没有做过这样的事 你呢\NI've never done anything\Nlike that before. Have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做过 也就一两次吧\NYeah, once or twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我该送你回家了\NSo, I guess I should take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 你想不想去派对玩呢\NHey, you don't want to go to a party, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德里克一定不能知道这事\NDerek can never know about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你开心吗\NYou happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.16,0:21:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-非常 -很好\N-Very. -Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在该高兴高兴了\NNow it's time to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.06,0:21:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位需要涂一下\NThis one needs to get painted up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脸还是身体呢\NFace or body?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.23,0:21:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身体\NBody.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要冰\NI need ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿\NI got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.52,0:22:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\NAll done.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.99,0:22:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很棒\NNice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.75,0:23:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上它就出现在我的钥匙环上\NIt just showed up there on my key ring this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.99,0:23:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我问过我爸是不是他放的\NI asked my dad if he put it there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.36,0:23:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他说他不清楚是哪的\Nbut he said he didn't know anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.89,0:23:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-只是把钥匙对吧 -是的 但不是我的\N- It's just a key, right?\N- Yeah, but it's not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.53,0:23:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我不知道哪来的是开哪的\NAnd I don't know how it got there or what it's for.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.90,0:23:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想我们离开这里出去想想吗\NYou want to leave so we can figure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.40,0:23:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万圣节快乐\NHappy Halloween!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.24,0:23:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以等等的\NIt can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.38,0:23:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以等一会儿\NIt can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.42,0:23:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.82,0:23:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-说什么 -谢谢\N- What? - Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.76,0:23:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢什么\NFor what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.93,0:23:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有这一切\NFor everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.94,0:25:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.61,0:25:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 我亲过你\NHey! I kissed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.81,0:25:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的你亲过 你叫什么名字\NYeah, you kind of did.\NWhat's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.68,0:25:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫凯特琳\NI'm Caitlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.15,0:25:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯特琳\NCaitlin...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.18,0:25:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天 你是凯特琳\NOh, my God. You're Caitlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.75,0:25:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我刚告诉你的\NI know! I just told you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.32,0:25:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我知道 我是说知道\NNo, I know... I just...I mean, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.59,0:25:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和你的女友 她\NYou and your girlfriend. She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.46,0:25:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-她死了 -是的\N- She died. - Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.56,0:25:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗\NAre you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.03,0:25:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是的 我真的醉了 -好吧\N- Yeah! I'm really drunk. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.70,0:25:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想跳舞吗\NDo you want to dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.90,0:25:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.81,0:25:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和真的不能比\NNot as good as the real ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.95,0:26:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀伤力也是\NOr as lethal.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.92,0:26:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 当然 我活该\NOkay, sure. I deserve that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.05,0:26:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么说都对\NI deserve basically everything you say about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.79,0:26:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要知道 是我把设备安装好的\NBut, you know, I was pretty instrumental setting this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.09,0:26:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部这些吗?\NAll this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.90,0:26:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我想去锐舞派对\NIf I wanted to go to a rave,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.50,0:26:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会乘时光机回到九十年代\NI'd get in a time machine and go back to the '90s.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.81,0:26:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看见斯科特了吗\NDid you see Scott?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.95,0:26:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\NYep.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.25,0:26:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉他发生什么了吗\NYou tell him what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.65,0:26:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有 我们还有几个小时时间记得吗\NNo. We still have a couple hours, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.48,0:26:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们答应过我爸\NWe promised my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.65,0:26:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你答应过你爸\NYou promised your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.05,0:26:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我答应他是为了保护他\NI promised him in order to protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.69,0:26:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你答应的\NYou did.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.02,0:26:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可没有\NI didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.52,0:26:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保护我爸是件坏事吗\NIs protecting my father such a bad thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.49,0:26:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢对斯科特有所隐瞒\NI don't like keeping secrets from Scott.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.33,0:26:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 你不会的\NNo, you don't,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.80,0:26:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢尴尬的站在这里\Nyou just like to stand there awkwardly
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.37,0:26:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等着有人注意到我们\Nwaiting for someone to notice us...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.00,0:26:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论我们是\NWhatever we are...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.77,0:26:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后你总是让事情\NAnd then you like to make things
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.81,0:27:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信的不对劲起来\Nincredibly uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.28,0:27:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么意思\NAnd what's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.68,0:27:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得是什么意思\NWhat do you think it means?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.88,0:27:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想意味着你可能生气了\NI think it means\Nyou're probably mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.25,0:27:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我没有生气 -没有吗\N-I'm not mad. -No?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.95,0:27:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-没有 -好吧\N-No. -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.35,0:27:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很沮丧\NI'm frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.12,0:27:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,性事吗\NSexually?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.50,0:27:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不介意我用一下吧\NMind if I borrow this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.55,0:27:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是想继续聊斯科特\NDo you want to talk about Scott
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.85,0:27:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是想在我的身体上作画\Nor do you want to paint my body?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.35,0:27:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想涂你的身体\NI want to paint your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.27,0:28:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 终于\NOh! Finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.11,0:28:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诡异\NAwkwardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.78,0:28:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然\NPredictably.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.34,0:28:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯科特\NScott...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.38,0:28:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯科特\NScott!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.59,0:30:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是伊桑吗 -艾登\N- Ethan? - Aiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.66,0:30:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊桑去哪里了\NWhere's Ethan?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.76,0:30:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也在找他\NI'm looking for him too.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.09,0:30:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都半个小时没见他了\NI haven't seen him in like half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.53,0:30:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不对吗\NIs something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.56,0:30:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾登\NAiden?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.03,0:30:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾登\NAiden?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.54,0:30:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有开瓶器吗\NYou have a bottle opener?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.20,0:30:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.01,0:30:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你钥匙上有荧光粉\NYour key has phosphors on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.84,0:30:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞧\NLook.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.66,0:30:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你喜欢女的\NUh, I thought you liked girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.53,0:31:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是喜欢女的 你呢\NI do like girls. Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.53,0:31:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-当然 -很好\N- Absolutely. - Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.27,0:31:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-所以你也喜欢男的吗 -是的\N- So you also like boys? - Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.04,0:31:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢\NDo you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.15,0:31:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 荧光粉是什么\NI am sorry. What are phosphors?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.48,0:31:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 它们可以是任何发光的物质\NOh, they're any substance that luminesces.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.59,0:31:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你的牙齿上和指甲里\NIt's in your teeth and your fingernails.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.46,0:31:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗衣粉\NLaundry detergent.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.12,0:31:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它也在这里\NIt's also in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.23,0:31:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在紫外线灯下它会反应所以会发亮\NReacts to the UV light, that's why it glows.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.27,0:31:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是怎么把荧光粉弄到钥匙上的呢\NHow would I get phosphors on my key?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.11,0:31:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有接触化学品吗\NHave you been handling chemicals?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.11,0:31:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有 我不认为我\NNo, I don't think I...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.05,0:31:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起 非常抱歉\NI'm sorry. I'm really, totally sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.49,0:32:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我刚想到些事 我必须走了\NI just thought of something and I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.82,0:32:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的 我想这样 我想留下\NReally, I want it. I want to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.46,0:32:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本来整晚留下的 我发誓\NI would just stay all night...I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.06,0:32:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我真的必须走 我无意冒犯你\NBut I really have to go and\NI don't want to offend you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.86,0:32:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好的 -抱歉 我\N- Okay. - Sorry. I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.47,0:32:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗 好的\NOkay? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.37,0:32:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你 你应该喝这个\NHere. You could drink that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.70,0:32:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都喝掉 全部好吗\NDrink that whole thing. Whole thing, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.54,0:32:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 再见\NExcuse me. Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.32,0:32:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沾了些涂料\NYou got some paint on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.79,0:32:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-还在那 -哦\N- Still there. - Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.76,0:32:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我来吧\NAh, let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.87,0:32:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，我的天\NOh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.37,0:32:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不敢相信你刚刚表现的和我妈一样\NI can't believe you just mommed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.61,0:32:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有\NI did not mom you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.81,0:32:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你绝对很像我妈\NYou totally mommed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.28,0:33:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，可能有点像\NOkay, I might have slightly mommed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.15,0:33:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么能接受得了这些?\NHow are you so okay with all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.59,0:33:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你看了那张照片\NI showed you a picture
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.09,0:33:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那会把其他人吓跑的\Nthat would send anybody else running the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.89,0:33:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我而言看起来不坏\NIt didn't look that bad to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.16,0:33:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看起来就像个恶魔\NI look like a demon from hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.43,0:33:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我看到了其他的东西\NI guess I saw something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.03,0:33:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了什么\NWhat did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.04,0:33:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来 呃 有些东西保护着你\NIt kind of looks like it's, uh, protecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.04,0:33:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像盔甲一样\NKind of like armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.88,0:33:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且对我而言也不像恶魔\NAnd it doesn't look like a demon to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.31,0:33:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得像什么\NWhat do you think it looks like?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.15,0:33:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像一只狐狸\NIt looks like a fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.85,0:34:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.01,0:34:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\NWhat's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.35,0:34:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你头上有点东西\NThere's something on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.48,0:34:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你耳朵后面\NBehind your ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.89,0:34:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,转过来看镜子\NTurn to the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.66,0:34:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到没\NYou see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.73,0:34:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么\NWhat is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.93,0:34:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来像个数字五\NLooks like a number five.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.91,0:34:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听到了吗\NDid you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.35,0:34:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾登，过这来\NAiden, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.72,0:34:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉迪亚\NLydia?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.86,0:34:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉迪亚\NLydia?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.46,0:34:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉迪亚 发生什么了\NLydia? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.53,0:34:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她怎么了\NWhat happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.76,0:35:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道，但他浑身发冷\NI don't know, but she's freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.06,0:35:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她体温过低了\NShe's practically hypothermic.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.43,0:35:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们把她扶进去 帮我一把\NWe gotta get her inside. Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.40,0:35:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去那边 那边有个暖风口\NOver here. There's a heating vent.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.28,0:35:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去找条毯子\NI'll try to find a blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.48,0:35:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.65,0:35:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有这样他才能自愈\NIt'll trigger the healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.75,0:35:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉迪亚\NLydia?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.69,0:35:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们衍生自黑暗\NThey came out of the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.63,0:35:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来一样\NIt's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.99,0:35:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一模一样\NExactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.25,0:35:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德里克?\NDerek?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.10,0:36:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(646,55)\c&HFEEC00&}Bloody Beetroot是2006下半年成立的意大利电子和舞曲朋克的音乐形式
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.10,0:36:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老兄 对不起Bloody Beetroot不接受要求\NBro, sorry, The Bloody Beetroot doesn't take requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.77,0:36:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老兄 说真的DJ不接受...\NBro, seriously. I said the DJ doesn't take...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.34,0:36:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会听我的\NHe'll take mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.25,0:36:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滚出去!\NGet out!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.13,0:36:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快滚远点\NGet her out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.37,0:36:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到斯科特\NFind Scott.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.55,0:37:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小伙伴们 他们都在看着我\NGuys, they're all looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.86,0:37:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他们都看我?\NWhy are they all looking at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.44,0:37:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伙伴们?\NGuys?
